Nowadays lectures are held more and more frequently in colleges and universities. The topics and categories of lectures become more and more diversified. As a result, traditional lecture system cant meet the new requirements. The implementation of Xiamen University Encyclopedia Lecture System based on Python is given. System targets, technical scheme, requirements analysis, design and implementation are introduced to provide a method to build a lecture system. It is aimed at exploring how to create a lecture system with all-sided functions such as efficiency exact lecture search and lecture application flow simplification.